; Test commodity comparison with different lot tags
; Covers commodity.cc (one has tag, other doesn't)
; (both have tags, comparing lexically)

2024/01/01 Buy with tag
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00} (alpha)
    Assets:Cash        $-1500.00

2024/01/02 Buy without tag
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash         $-750.00

2024/01/03 Buy with different tag
    Assets:Brokerage    3 AAPL {$150.00} (beta)
    Assets:Cash         $-450.00

test bal --no-total --lots Brokerage
    5 AAPL {$150.00}
10 AAPL {$150.00} (alpha)
3 AAPL {$150.00} (beta)  Assets:Brokerage
end test
